Welcome to my API:

Steps to run:
1. open the terminal and navigate to the project directory
2. $set FLASK_APP=hello
3. $flask run

Valid endpoints:
GET: localhost:5000/show
will display all the pets currently stored

POST: localhost:5000/add/name-to-add
will add the pet name to the stored list

PUT: localhost:5000/old-name/new-name
will rename the pet with the new name

DELETE: localhost:5000/yeet/name-to-remove
will remove the pet given